text: Othon Moskhidis (born 5 February 1942) is a Greek wrestler. He competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Greek male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Greece Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
